  "title": "Dental Clinic Assistant - Central - 5 days (start Jan 2026) [GC]",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide frontline customer service.</li>\n  <li>Scheduling of appointment and patent registration.</li>\n  <li>Handling phone calls and inquiries.</li>\n  <li>Process medical insurances, tax invoices and payment collection.</li>\n  <li>Handle administrative, clinical duties, simple procedures and ad-hoc duties.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>With a minimum of 1 year experience as Clinic Assistant.</li>\n  <li>Possess good communication and interpersonal skills.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
